{"tid":2355853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳台灣駐港辦官員遭拘捕 陸委會：相關消息非事實","createTime":"2021-01-06T11:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T11:26:06.000Z","uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85e52237e750848de8537e05906ac203ed7f374f","tid":2355853,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">傳駐港辦官員遭拘捕 陸委會：相關消息非事實</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/01/06 17:46<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者賴言曦台北6日電）<span class=\"red\">香港警方上午大規模拘捕泛民派人士後，有消息指台灣駐港辦事處有官員也遭拘捕。陸委會下午強調，相關消息並非事實，駐港辦事處運作如常。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港警方今天上午大規模拘捕超過50名泛民派人士，並搜索立場新聞等媒體辦公室、曾在去年協助民主派舉行「35+」初選計畫的「香港民意研究所」等機構。然而稍早曾有消息稱，台灣駐港辦事處也有官員遭港警拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n大陸委員會下午以書面形式澄清，指出網傳駐港辦事處官員在香港遭拘捕，並非事實，駐港辦事處仍運作如常，消息來源也已自行刪除貼文。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會也再度重申，台灣駐港機構提供的服務，有利維繫台港交流及保障兩地民眾權益，各方應以民眾福祉為念，共同維持台港良性互動。（編輯：繆宗翰）1100106<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101060290.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202101060290.aspx&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=96f90a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101060290.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c22dc6028b36196221e1bede571a415f525bac0d","tid":2355853,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"有心人士在製造假消息"},{"pid":"437327ace2461587df80b8d320909b0ef01eb0a6","tid":2355853,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">港警今晨大逮捕50多名民主人士 陸委會：東方明珠變「東方煉獄」</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3402759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402759&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=bb7e3f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402759&h=202836dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3402759</a>"},{"pid":"6186f3c81696779287b8416d9792cc4b3dd5131a","tid":2355853,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ws.mac.gov.tw/001/Upload/299/relpic/8520/70216/f94fdeb1-d9a5-4ea6-9046-261b96a345d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fws.mac.gov.tw%2F001%2FUpload%2F299%2Frelpic%2F8520%2F70216%2Ff94fdeb1-d9a5-4ea6-9046-261b96a345d6.png&h=17814f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台北經濟文化辦事處 (香港辦事處)<br />\n<br />\n地址：香港金鐘道89號力寶中心第1座40樓<br />\n電話：(+852) 2525-8642<br />\n服務信箱：service@teco.org.hk"}]}